<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News]]></title><link/> https://sputniknews.com/新闻<atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/sputniknews" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RSSHub</generator><webmaster> i@diygod.me (DIY神)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 5 月 21 日，星期日 18:44:08 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[Turkish Interior Minister Accuses Sweden of Electoral Meddling]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110507005" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0e/1110354139_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_4a5c25afd37606e16e44cd36a067de0d.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110354121" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/turkish-interior-minister-accuses-sweden-of-electoral-meddling-1110507005.html?share-img=1110354121"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Pavel Bednyakov</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">一名选民在总统和议会选举期间将选票投入投票站的投票箱</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="A voter drops the ballots into the ballot box at the polling station during the presidential and parliamentary elections - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="在总统和议会选举期间，选民将选票投入投票站的投票箱" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0e/1110354139_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_243d52b691a3e4dc96abe3bd1ab7b8e0.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0e/1110354139_0:160:3072:1888_640x0_80_0_0_3744d0619132dc3d2c82e354b23900b7.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0e/1110354139_0:160:3072:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_90ebb4bca98031f6299d8bc47fff8858.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/0e/1110354139_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_243d52b691a3e4dc96abe3bd1ab7b8e0.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / 帕维尔贝德尼亚科夫</div>/ </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据安卡拉（人造卫星）网报道：土耳其内政部长苏莱曼·索伊卢指责瑞典干预该国的选举，因为新总统的投票将在下周日进入决选阶段。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Soylu 是总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安 (Recep Tayyip Erdogan) 所在的正义与发展党 (AKP) 党的成员，他指责瑞典 Oyve Otesi（投票与超越）的选举监督员<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/over-470000-turkish-voters-cast-ballots-abroad-in-presidential-runoff--1110493105.html" target="_blank">在投票站向选民</a>施加压力。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"><p> “瑞典国家正在资助这个 Oy ve Otesi 协会。寄钱给它，但为什么？干涉 Turkiye 的选举。这是如此明显和明确，”这位部长在伊斯坦布尔的一次竞选集会上说，正如 Aydinlik 报纸所引述的那样. </p></div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110507005" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/turkish-interior-minister-accuses-sweden-of-electoral-meddling-1110507005.html?share-block=1110507007" data-title="&amp;quot;The Swedish state is funding this Oy ve Otesi association. Sending it money, but why? To interfere in the election in Turkiye. It is so obvious and clear,&amp;quot; the minister told a campaign rally in Istanbul, as quoted by the Aydinlik newspaper."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> Soylu 以其对西方的严厉批评而闻名。他周三指责美国试图影响选举， <a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230517/erdogan-to-prioritize-tv-appearances-in-preparation-for-presidential-runoff---reports-1110416330.html" target="_blank">埃尔多安</a>和他的反对派挑战者凯末尔·基利达罗格鲁将在 5 月 28 日的第二轮选举中对决。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 21 May 2023 18:35:56 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/turkish-interior-minister-accuses-sweden-of-electoral-meddling-1110507005.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/turkish-interior-minister-accuses-sweden-of-electoral-meddling-1110507005.html<category>世界</category><category>突厥耶</category><category>雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安</category><category>苏莱曼大豆</category><category>凯末尔·基利达罗格鲁</category><category>瑞典</category><category>正义与发展党 (AKP)</category><category> 2023 年土耳其总统选举</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Ukrainian Forces Shell Artemovsk With Mortars After Its Liberation by Russia - Video]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110506466" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110506306_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_3188af8139029d62bc8c62343bed7158.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110506288" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/ukrainian-forces-shell-artemovsk-with-mortars-after-its-liberation-by-russia---video-1110506466.html?share-img=1110506288"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Correspondent</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">阿尔杰莫夫斯克 (Bakhmut) 的废墟，在俄罗斯和乌克兰军队之间的激烈战斗中。 2023 年 5 月 19 日。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="Ruins of Artemovsk (Bakhmut) amid fierce fighting between Russian and Ukrainian forces. May 19, 2023. - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="俄罗斯和乌克兰军队之间的激烈战斗中的 Artemovsk（巴赫穆特）废墟。 2023 年 5 月 19 日。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110506306_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_0d525624cfd0c46d7c41a982ff95854b.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110506306_0:160:3072:1888_640x0_80_0_0_486e135e807a8fbedbedd455a9a6a59d.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110506306_0:160:3072:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_de512644cbfc2e19b6c903e810e38410.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110506306_0:160:3072:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_0d525624cfd0c46d7c41a982ff95854b.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> ©人造卫星/通讯员</div>/ </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">伊利亚楚卡诺夫</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_tsukanov_ilya/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:i.tsukanov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">具有战略意义的顿涅茨克北部地区城市阿尔杰莫夫斯克（也称为巴赫穆特）周六被俄罗斯军方和瓦格纳集团的部队完全解放，据信数万名乌克兰军队和外国雇佣兵被埋在该城市的废墟中。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在俄罗斯军队完全解放阿尔乔莫夫斯克市后，乌克兰军队向阿尔乔莫夫斯克的公寓楼发射迫击炮，显然是为了炸毁在这座城市的高层建筑上展开的俄罗斯国旗。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “一旦他们下达命令，我们一占领九层楼，也就是我们所说的‘俄罗斯方块’，就立即竖起我们的旗帜，向全世界展示这是我们的土地，而不是某种国家的土地。纳粹分子及其同类，”其中一名战士告诉萨莫莱特区的一名人造卫星记者，这是阿尔杰莫夫斯克最后一个被清除的地区。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “昨天，当我们刚刚在九层楼上插上旗帜时，敌人立即决定用120毫米和82毫米口径的迫击炮将其击倒。他们什么都试过了，但如你所知，我们有力量站在我们这边，所以他们失败了。正如他们所说，无论俄罗斯人在哪里竖起他们的国旗，那都是我们的领土，”这名战士说。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110506466" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/ukrainian-forces-shell-artemovsk-with-mortars-after-its-liberation-by-russia---video-1110506466.html?share-block=1110506469" data-title="“Yesterday, when we had just put up our flag on the nine story building, the enemy immediately decided to knock it down using 120 mm and 82 mm caliber mortars. They tried everything, but as you know, we have power on our side, so they failed. As they say, wherever Russians put up their flag, that’s our territory,” the fighter said."></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social" data-social="telegram"><div class="article__tg"></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">经过 224 天的逐个街区、挨家挨户的残酷战斗，俄罗斯军队于 5 月 20 日完成了对阿尔捷莫夫斯克的解放。这座城市战前人口约为 70,000 人，是重要的区域交通枢纽，从 2015 年开始被乌克兰军队变成了一座看似坚不可摧的堡垒，由数千吨混凝土和开采的混凝土加固。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">阿尔乔莫夫斯克的解放预计将使前线远离顿涅茨克，有望缓解这座城市在九年多的时间里遭受乌克兰炮击的苦难。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social" data-social="telegram"><div class="article__tg"></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">城市的战斗已将其变成当地平民的地狱。星期六，另一名战士告诉卫星通讯社，一名老人离开他避难的地下室前往俄罗斯一侧撤离，但在距离俄罗斯防线仅 50 米处被乌克兰炮击中，当场死亡。 “他在整个战争中幸存下来，但最后死在了最后——就在巴赫穆特被占领之前，”这名战士<a href="https://t.me/rian_ru/203305" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">说</a>。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">参加战斗的俄罗斯军队估计，有超过 30,000 名乌克兰士兵和外国雇佣军在为这座城市而战中丧生，泽连斯基总统曾将这座城市称为“我们士气的堡垒”。乌克兰总统在 3 月份<a href="https://www.latimes.com/world-nation/story/2023-03-06/ukraine-unyielding-in-bakhmut-as-russian-troops-close-in" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">拒绝</a>下令从阿尔杰莫夫斯克撤退，因为很明显俄罗斯军队会占领它，俄罗斯军方随后报告说，乌克兰军队和雇佣军在数周内<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230429/moscow-ukraine-loses-nearly-600-military-mercenaries-in-donetsk-direction-over-past-day-1109952145.html" target="_blank">每天</a>因俄罗斯炮兵、空袭和无人机袭击造成<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230513/ukraine-loses-almost-300-military-mercenaries-in-donetsk-direction-over-past-day---moscow-1110316273.html" target="_blank">数百</a>人伤亡.</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">泽连斯基周六证实，阿尔乔莫夫斯克已经失传，称这座城市已被摧毁，现在“只留在我们心中”。他的新闻办公室继续摆出勇敢的姿态，保证总统的话并不是承认这座城市已经投降。乌克兰国防部副部长汉娜·马利亚尔声称战斗仍在继续，乌克兰军队“控制了一些工业和基础设施以及萨莫莱特地区 Bakhmut 的独立住宅区。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">俄罗斯军方周六证实<a href="https://t.me/mod_russia/26733" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">，</a> “在阿尔捷莫夫斯克的战术方向上，由于瓦格纳突击分队在南方部队的炮兵和航空兵支援下的进攻行动，已经完成了对阿尔捷莫夫斯克市的解放。”</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 21 May 2023 17:53:37 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/ukrainian-forces-shell-artemovsk-with-mortars-after-its-liberation-by-russia---video-1110506466.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/ukrainian-forces-shell-artemovsk-with-mortars-after-its-liberation-by-russia---video-1110506466.html<category>俄罗斯在乌克兰的特别行动</category><category>沃洛德米尔·泽伦斯基</category><category>乌克兰</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>通讯员</category><category>视频</category><category>镜头</category><category>旗帜</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Russian Pacific Fleet: Three Centuries Keeping Window to the East Open]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110504440" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503388_0:0:3071:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_045c2cb710aae8ca5ca763ab8a561c16.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110503370" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/russian-pacific-fleet-three-centuries-keeping-window-to-the-east-open-1110504440.html?share-img=1110503370"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Ильдус Гилязутдинов</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">俄罗斯太平洋舰队的军人在符拉迪沃斯托克庆祝海军日。档案照片。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="Servicemen of the Russian Pacific Fleet celebrate Navy Day in Vladivostok. File photo. - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="俄罗斯太平洋舰队的军人在符拉迪沃斯托克庆祝海军日。档案照片。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503388_0:161:3071:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_b58c40381af64901a49ceaf9edbe7ba0.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503388_0:161:3071:1888_640x0_80_0_0_de03aad765b482fbff34b78fab691716.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503388_0:161:3071:1888_1280x0_80_0_0_830d7004b7d25831029107d0674925af.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503388_0:161:3071:1888_1920x0_80_0_0_b58c40381af64901a49ceaf9edbe7ba0.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Ильдус Γилязутдинов</div> / </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">伊利亚楚卡诺夫</div><div class="article__author-links"> <a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_tsukanov_ilya/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a> <a data-modal-open="feedback_author" href="mailto:i.tsukanov@sputniknews.com" title="写给作者">写给作者</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">5 月 21 日是俄罗斯太平洋舰队精神先驱鄂霍次克舰队成立 292 周年。将近三个世纪过去了，这支海军的使命始终如一——保卫俄罗斯的远东边界，为国家提供进入太平洋温暖水域的通道。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 292 年前的今天，即 1731 年 5 月 21 日，女皇安娜·约安诺夫娜 (Anna Ioannovna) 颁布了一项关于在俄罗斯远东地区建立新的海军力量的法令。这支舰队总部设在鄂霍次克的哈巴罗夫斯克边疆区定居点，其任务是守卫俄罗斯帝国远东属地的海岸和岛屿。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social" data-social="telegram"><div class="article__tg"></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在鄂霍次克创建了一个小型造船厂，以建造用于在鄂霍次克和堪察加半岛之间运送货物和人员的船只，俄罗斯国家和地方实业家建造和租用商业、科学和军用船只来绘制当地水域，向南探索日本，向东探索朝向阿拉斯加和加利福尼亚的海岸，俄罗斯定居者<a href="https://www.colonialvoyage.com/russians-in-america-alaska-california/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">很快将在那里建立多个殖民地</a>。 1799 年，俄罗斯的帕维尔一世宣布建立一支正规海军部队，以保护俄罗斯在该地区的财产。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>在接下来的 150 年里，该舰队的总部多次搬迁，1849 年迁往堪察加彼得罗巴甫洛夫斯克，1855 年迁往阿穆尔河畔尼古拉耶夫斯克（当时舰队更名为西伯利亚舰队），从 1871 年起，在港口城市符拉迪沃斯托克。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">这支舰队在 1854 年 8 月和 9 月进行了第一次海上交战，当时俄罗斯在克里米亚战争期间与奥斯曼帝国、法国和大英帝国交锋，护卫舰极光号、德维纳武装运输舰和堪察加彼得罗巴甫洛夫斯克驻军对峙对抗由六艘英国和法国军舰组成的中队。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="media"><div class="article__media"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="photo"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110504440" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503568_0:0:1480:925_1440x900_80_0_1_06158fda8ca645277de16f742c79f83a.jpg?source-sid=not_sputnik_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110503550" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/russian-pacific-fleet-three-centuries-keeping-window-to-the-east-open-1110504440.html?share-img=1110503550"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© 照片：Alexey Bogolyubov</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">彼得罗巴甫洛夫斯克港防御工事，1854 年 9 月。俄罗斯画家 Alexey Bogolyubov（1824-1896）的画作。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="photo" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="Defense of Petropavlovsk port, September 1854. Painting by Russian painter Alexey Bogolyubov (1824-1896). - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="彼得罗巴甫洛夫斯克港防御战，1854 年 9 月。俄罗斯画家 Alexey Bogolyubov（1824-1896 年）的画作。" class=" lazyload" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503568_0:0:1480:925_1920x0_80_0_0_b1009340bda7b7887aefee203348eea0.jpg" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20width=%221920%22%20height=%221200%22%3E%3C/svg%3E 100w" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1200" data-srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503568_0:0:1480:925_640x0_80_0_0_156ccc197545385f482567fedf2f2aec.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503568_0:0:1480:925_1280x0_80_0_0_a9ce044f89f9c5253e94d428e0bef3fd.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503568_0:0:1480:925_1920x0_80_0_0_b1009340bda7b7887aefee203348eea0.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__description " data-nosnippet="">彼得罗巴甫洛夫斯克港防御战，1854 年 9 月。俄罗斯画家 Alexey Bogolyubov（1824-1896 年）的画作。 </div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 照片 : Alexey Bogolyubov </div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">现在被称为太平洋舰队的海军将在俄罗斯 20 世纪的历史中发挥至关重要的作用。在 1904 年至 1905 年的日俄战争开始时，一支只有 4 艘巡洋舰、5 艘炮艇、22 艘鱼雷艇和 2 艘布雷艇的西伯利亚舰队与配备战列舰、巡洋舰和驱逐舰的日本舰队对峙，促使尼古拉二世皇帝派遣波罗的海舰队踏上令人筋疲力尽的环球之旅，与日本帝国军队对峙。 1905 年 5 月，在灾难性的对马海战中损失了大部分舰队，迫使俄罗斯求和并引发了第一次俄国革命。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">装备有 Askold 装甲巡洋舰（参加过日俄战争）、一艘轻型巡洋舰、两打驱逐舰和 13 艘潜艇的西伯利亚舰队在第一次世界大战中在物质上得到加强，但在政治上士气低落。 1917 年十月革命后，舰队的大部分船只被日本占领军和白军扣押。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="media"><div class="article__media"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="photo"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110504440" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503749_0:0:1024:727_1440x900_80_0_1_49ea32166ad7a74362abf46b101b55b5.jpg?source-sid=Wikipedia " data-photoview-image-id="1110503731" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/russian-pacific-fleet-three-centuries-keeping-window-to-the-east-open-1110504440.html?share-img=1110503731"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© <a href="http://www.wikipedia.org/" title="维基百科">Wikipedia</a> / Shobido &amp; Co / US LOC</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">日本关于占领俄罗斯远东地区的宣传海报。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="photo" data-source-sid="Wikipedia " alt="Japanese propaganda poster on the occupation of the Russian Far East. - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="日本占领俄罗斯远东地区的宣传海报。" class=" lazyload" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503749_0:0:1024:727_1920x0_80_0_0_ac9d4581ed2de2549e30be52fb699d94.jpg" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20width=%221920%22%20height=%221363%22%3E%3C/svg%3E 100w" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1363" data-srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503749_0:0:1024:727_640x0_80_0_0_75319a7f6f44499eb09628a37df6a9b6.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503749_0:0:1024:727_1280x0_80_0_0_1f8e7034797c2d5361fe2dcaa51b2840.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503749_0:0:1024:727_1920x0_80_0_0_ac9d4581ed2de2549e30be52fb699d94.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__description " data-nosnippet="">日本占领俄罗斯远东地区的宣传海报。 </div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © <a href="http://www.wikipedia.org/" title="维基百科">Wikipedia</a> / Shobido &amp; Co / US LOC</div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2"> 1935 年：Fleet 获得现在的名称</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">1921年俄国内战结束后，苏联当局慢慢开始重建舰队的工作。太平洋舰队于 1935 年 1 月获得现名，当时苏联在目睹日本侵略满洲后，意识到东京可能会成为下一个针对苏联的目标，并开始大规模扩军。莫斯科不可能集聚与日本（当时拥有世界<a href="https://ww2db.com/other.php?other_id=5" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">第三强大的</a>海军）同样的海军力量，因此转而专注于不对称战争，包括大量小型鱼雷艇和潜艇，作为后盾由海防部队和海军航空兵。除了太平洋舰队外，苏联于 1939 年 8 月成立了北太平洋舰队，以守卫将俄罗斯大陆与库页岛隔开的鞑靼海峡。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>第二次世界大战期间，太平洋舰队<a href="https://lend-lease.net/articles-en/the-unknown-world-war-ii-in-the-northern-pacific/">参与了</a>确保美国租借援助通过太平洋安全通过太平洋的行动。超过 147,000 名舰队人员被调往西部，加入北方舰队的海军部队、其他海军编队和地面部队，与纳粹及其盟友作战，参与保卫莫斯科、斯大林格勒和塞瓦斯托波尔。</p></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">在 1945 年的八月风暴行动中，太平洋舰队协助红军进攻满洲和朝鲜，攻击位于朝鲜沿海基地和港口的日军，并进行多次海军登陆，最著名的是从南库页岛解放该岛南部的行动日军。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="media"><div class="article__media"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="photo"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110504440" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503927_0:0:3000:1996_1440x900_80_0_1_115f47c06cbb45c3e47e86ad9ce6c39b.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110503909" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/russian-pacific-fleet-three-centuries-keeping-window-to-the-east-open-1110504440.html?share-img=1110503909"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Evgeny Haldey</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">1945 年 8 月。日本占领的中国哈尔滨市的居民在解放后迎接苏联太平洋舰队海军步兵。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="photo" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="August 1945. Residents of the Japanese-occupied city of Harbin, China greet Soviet Pacific Fleet naval infantry following their liberation. - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="1945 年 8 月。日本占领的中国哈尔滨市的居民在解放后迎接苏联太平洋舰队海军步兵。" class=" lazyload" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503927_0:0:3000:1996_1920x0_80_0_0_7bb605b355250bba1ac577e56ce4a8eb.jpg" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20width=%221920%22%20height=%221277%22%3E%3C/svg%3E 100w" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1277" data-srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503927_0:0:3000:1996_640x0_80_0_0_244fc7d1fcfeb4afe859045506d05034.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503927_0:0:3000:1996_1280x0_80_0_0_580a00d4ee9adacada60af8c03a1080c.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110503927_0:0:3000:1996_1920x0_80_0_0_7bb605b355250bba1ac577e56ce4a8eb.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__description " data-nosnippet=""> 1945 年 8 月。日本占领的中国哈尔滨市的居民在解放后迎接苏联太平洋舰队海军步兵。 </div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Evgeny Haldey </div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">太平洋舰队积极参与了冷战，包括朝鲜战争，协助向朝鲜海军运送武器和军事装备。 1979 年，太平洋舰队在越南金兰湾建立了据点，该设施成为苏联最大的海外基地。冷战时期，太平洋舰队<a href="https://www.jstor.org/stable/43738012" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">成为苏联海军四大舰队中规模最大、实力最强的</a>，与北方舰队一起装备弹道导弹核潜艇，成为国家海军核力量的中坚力量威慑力。这支舰队在太平洋和印度洋以及阿拉伯海开展行动，使其责任范围比苏联其他海军的总和还要大。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="media"><div class="article__media"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="photo"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110504440" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/103988/85/1039888539_0:0:1200:914_1440x900_80_0_1_c229c1bf17b1c15f44e6e363a1a605fa.jpg?source-sid=Wikipedia " data-photoview-image-id="1039888538" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/russian-pacific-fleet-three-centuries-keeping-window-to-the-east-open-1110504440.html?share-img=1039888538"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© <a href="http://www.wikipedia.org/" title="维基百科">Wikipedia</a></span><span class="photoview__desc-text">苏联军舰停靠在越南金兰湾。美术师为 DIA 出版的名为“苏联军事力量”的小册子进行渲染。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="photo" data-source-sid="Wikipedia " alt="Cam Ranh Bay with Soviet Fleet, artist's rendering from 1985 - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="金兰湾与苏联舰队，1985 年的艺术家渲染图" class=" lazyload" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/103988/85/1039888539_0:0:1200:914_1920x0_80_0_0_a874bf7bef048919379e243d0e8e2b6b.jpg" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20width=%221920%22%20height=%221462%22%3E%3C/svg%3E 100w" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1462" data-srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/103988/85/1039888539_0:0:1200:914_640x0_80_0_0_b82a2dc79fbaa67d1e156cfa6941c8fb.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/103988/85/1039888539_0:0:1200:914_1280x0_80_0_0_fb1539953a871895c6ab89c0f272a744.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/103988/85/1039888539_0:0:1200:914_1920x0_80_0_0_a874bf7bef048919379e243d0e8e2b6b.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__description " data-nosnippet="">苏联军舰停靠在越南金兰湾。美术师为 DIA 出版的名为“苏联军事力量”的小册子进行渲染。 </div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> ©<a href="http://www.wikipedia.org/" title="维基百科">维基百科</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="h3"><h3 class="article__h2">堕落与重生</h3></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">太平洋舰队在 1991 年苏联解体时受到重创，其两艘重型飞机巡洋舰——明斯克号和新罗西斯克号——在中国被卖掉并变成了一个主题公园（明斯克号）并报废（在新罗西斯克的案例）。 Orlan 级重型核导弹巡洋舰 Admiral Lazarev 遭受了类似的命运，其他数十艘大大小小的船只也遭遇了类似的命运。从 1990 年代初期到 2003 年，舰队没有接收任何一艘新的大型军舰或潜艇。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="media"><div class="article__media"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="photo"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110504440" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110504104_0:0:2048:3130_1440x900_80_0_1_206cc4d9e5b9cc491d58901a83526ebb.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110504086" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/russian-pacific-fleet-three-centuries-keeping-window-to-the-east-open-1110504440.html?share-img=1110504086"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Vladimir Rodionov</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">苏联太平洋舰队的重型飞机巡洋舰新罗西斯克进行演习，1984 年。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="photo" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="Heavy aircraft-carrying cruiser Novorossiysk of the Soviet Pacific Fleet on maneuvers, 1984. - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="苏联太平洋舰队的重型飞机巡洋舰新罗西斯克进行演习，1984 年。" class="m-vertical lazyload" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110504104_0:0:2048:3130_1920x0_80_0_0_1fe051b0699cd3f868ac77052ec2bd5e.jpg" srcset="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22%20width=%221920%22%20height=%222934%22%3E%3C/svg%3E 100w" decoding="async" width="1920" height="2934" data-srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110504104_0:0:2048:3130_640x0_80_0_0_5b93cbf5589b16863ed1b45b5f7daa23.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110504104_0:0:2048:3130_1280x0_80_0_0_0e95c7cfc5db099df19a0201d00d60cb.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110504104_0:0:2048:3130_1920x0_80_0_0_1fe051b0699cd3f868ac77052ec2bd5e.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__description " data-nosnippet="">苏联太平洋舰队的重型飞机巡洋舰新罗西斯克进行演习，1984 年。 </div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Vladimir Rodionov </div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">直到 2000 年代后期，才开始投入大量资源，现有船只得到升级，舰队获得新船只。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">如今，舰队拥有 11 艘主要水面战舰，包括作为舰队旗舰的 1164 号亚特兰特瓦良格巡洋舰、五艘驱逐舰、五艘护卫舰、大约二十艘反潜战和导弹护卫舰、四艘大型两栖攻击艇、四艘Borey 级核导弹潜艇，以及大约 18 艘攻击和巡航导弹潜艇。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">上个月，俄罗斯海军总司令尼古拉·埃夫梅诺夫海军上将宣布，太平洋舰队将在未来几年继续重新武装，配备新的护卫舰、护卫舰和核潜艇。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “装备——最新的舰艇、潜艇和飞机，已经证明了高度的可靠性，而其人员也展示了其专业技能，”这位指挥官在 4 月中旬进行了快速战备检查后表示。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">预计在未来五年内加入舰队的新舰艇包括 12 艘 Project 20380 Steregushchiy 和 Project 20385 Gremyashchiy 级护卫舰、新的 Project 22800 卡拉库特级小型导弹舰，以及安装在升级后的 Kalibr 和 Uran 巡航导弹和反舰导弹11551M 海军上将维诺格拉多夫护卫舰项目。两艘 Project 22350 Admiral Gorshkov 级护卫舰目前也在圣彼得堡的 Severnaya Verf 建造中，预计分别于 2026 年和 2029 年服役。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">太平洋舰队的潜艇舰队预计将在今年年底之前再接收至少一艘改进型 Borey-A 核潜艇，并在 2024 年底之前配备 6 艘新的 Project 636.3 Varshavyanka 柴电攻击潜艇。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">最后，太平洋舰队等待升级其两栖攻击能力，两艘经过改装的 Project 11711 Ivan Gren 级大型登陆舰预计将于 2023 年和 2024 年服役。这些舰艇将能够搭载多达 40 辆装甲车、400 名士兵、或四到五架 Ka-52K、Ka-27 或 Ka-29 直升机，以及最多六架塞尔纳级登陆艇。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 21 May 2023 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/russian-pacific-fleet-three-centuries-keeping-window-to-the-east-open-1110504440.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/russian-pacific-fleet-three-centuries-keeping-window-to-the-east-open-1110504440.html<category>军队</category><category>太平洋</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>苏联</category><category>俄罗斯太平洋舰队</category><category>苏联海军</category><category>潜艇</category><category>船只</category><category>海军</category><category>俄罗斯海军</category><category>历史</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Estonia Says NATO Fighter Jets Will Move to Latvia During Air Base Repairs in 2024]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110506033" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105308/04/1053080495_0:0:1579:1022_1440x900_80_0_1_00038250f00d4ed2d89550ea8874edf9.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1053080494" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/estonia-says-nato-fighter-jets-will-move-to-latvia-during-air-base-repairs-in-2024-1110506033.html?share-img=1053080494"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo /</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">在这张由视频制作的图片中，两架 F35A 战斗机停在爱沙尼亚哈朱马阿马里空军基地的停机坪上，2017 年 4 月 25 日，星期二</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="In this image made from video, two F35A fighter jets sit on the tarmac at the Amari Airbase in Harjumaa, Estonia, Tuesday, April 25, 2017 - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="在这张由视频制作的图片中，两架 F35A 战斗机停在爱沙尼亚哈朱马阿马里空军基地的停机坪上，2017 年 4 月 25 日，星期二" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105308/04/1053080495_0:134:1579:1022_1920x0_80_0_0_6743ebbdfff70a27f6e56171dbfa50a7.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105308/04/1053080495_0:134:1579:1022_640x0_80_0_0_440ab45ff69aeef2424a2a534257bfa9.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105308/04/1053080495_0:134:1579:1022_1280x0_80_0_0_70d226a387da0b6778f25b78ce2622cf.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105308/04/1053080495_0:134:1579:1022_1920x0_80_0_0_6743ebbdfff70a27f6e56171dbfa50a7.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 美联社照片 / </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：爱沙尼亚国防部周日表示，由于阿马里空军基地的重建，北约负责波罗的海领空的战斗机将于明年暂时从爱沙尼亚转移到拉脱维亚。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “爱沙尼亚的阿马里空军基地将在 2024 年进行重建，在此期间，波罗的海空域将从拉脱维亚和立陶宛手中获得保障。重建完成后，盟军战斗机将返回爱沙尼亚，”该部表示。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110506033" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/estonia-says-nato-fighter-jets-will-move-to-latvia-during-air-base-repairs-in-2024-1110506033.html?share-block=1110506034" data-title="&quot;The Amari Air Base in Estonia will undergo reconstruction in 2024, during which the Baltic airspace will be secured from Latvia and Lithuania. After the reconstruction is completed, the allied fighter jets will return to Estonia,&quot; the ministry said. "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">声明中写道，北约的空中警务飞机将从 2024 年春季到秋季从<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230509/nato-airborne-units-arrive-in-estonia-for-swift-response-23-drill-1110220349.html" target="_blank">阿马里</a>转移到拉脱维亚的 Lielvarde 空军基地，同时部署在立陶宛 Siauliai 空军基地的盟军喷气式飞机也将确保空中安全。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">由于爱沙尼亚、拉脱维亚和立陶宛不拥有适合执行巡逻飞行的<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230511/us-f-22-raptor-fighters-reportedly-begin-training-flights-in-estonia-1110254339.html" target="_blank">飞机</a>，因此它们的北约盟国为它们提供了必要的能力。在四个月的轮换基础上，他们在波罗的海地区上空巡逻，波罗的海国家通过接待盟军飞机和提供必要的人员做出贡献。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 21 May 2023 16:42:38 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/estonia-says-nato-fighter-jets-will-move-to-latvia-during-air-base-repairs-in-2024-1110506033.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/estonia-says-nato-fighter-jets-will-move-to-latvia-during-air-base-repairs-in-2024-1110506033.html<category>军队</category><category>爱沙尼亚</category><category>拉脱维亚</category><category>阿玛瑞</category><category>爱沙尼亚国防部</category><category>北约</category><category>战斗机</category><category>北约基地</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[US Chipmaker Micron Fails Chinese Clearance Check]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110505795" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0a/07/1101597496_0:0:3072:2048_1440x900_80_0_1_136f99127da0669fa81801a358e61861.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1101597479" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/us-chipmaker-micron-fails-chinese-clearance-check-1110505795.html?share-img=1101597479"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Alexey Kudenko / 泽列诺格勒的美光工厂</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">泽列诺格勒的美光工厂</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="The Micron plant in Zelenograd - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="泽列诺格勒的美光工厂" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0a/07/1101597496_0:131:3073:1859_1920x0_80_0_0_5d73d70284abf76efcfaf19b3ee5e473.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0a/07/1101597496_0:131:3073:1859_640x0_80_0_0_5313ab01d2249b85c3b30b543ee32943.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0a/07/1101597496_0:131:3073:1859_1280x0_80_0_0_296d47baaae3e1795aea1e65a46dcfa3.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/0a/07/1101597496_0:131:3073:1859_1920x0_80_0_0_5d73d70284abf76efcfaf19b3ee5e473.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / Alexey Kudenko / 泽列诺格勒的美光工厂</div>/ </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据北京（人造卫星）网报道：中国国家互联网信息办公室周日宣布，美国芯片制造商美光科技被发现构成国家安全风险后，将被禁止向关键基础设施运营商销售产品。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “审查发现，美光的产品对网络安全构成了相当大的风险，使其成为该国关键信息基础设施供应链的主要安全威胁，可能影响国家安全，”声明中写道。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110505795" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/us-chipmaker-micron-fails-chinese-clearance-check-1110505795.html?share-block=1110505796" data-title="&quot;The review found that Micron’s products posed a considerable risk to network security, making it a major security threat to supply chains of the country’s critical information infrastructure that can affect the national security,&quot; the statement read. "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">监管机构强调，只要<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20210129/huawei-smic-to-join-chipmaking-standards-group-as-china-pushes-foreign-tech-decoupling-in-trade-war-1081919553.html" target="_blank">外国公司遵守法律，中国就会对它们保持开放</a>。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">英国一家商业报纸 4 月报道称，在韩国对美光展开安全调查后，美国要求韩国限制对中国<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230316/south-korea-to-create-worlds-largest-semiconductor-cluster---presidential-office-1108438916.html" target="_blank">的半导体</a>出口。中国外交部发言人毛宁称此次审查是“正常的监管措施”，并批评美国违反贸易规则。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 21 May 2023 16:37:18 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/us-chipmaker-micron-fails-chinese-clearance-check-1110505795.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/us-chipmaker-micron-fails-chinese-clearance-check-1110505795.html<category>世界</category><category>毛宁</category><category>中国</category><category>美光</category><category>我们</category><category>芯片</category><category>芯片制造商</category><category>半导体</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Moscow Says G7 'Irreversibly Degraded,' Summit's Decisions Politicized]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110505682" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110505668_0:0:2293:1529_1440x900_80_0_1_89f178f3681ccc6b83c5f69fa74420f2.jpg?source-sid=ap_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1110505509" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/moscow-says-g7-irreversibly-degraded-summits-decisions-politicized-1110505682.html?share-img=1110505509"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© AP Photo / Jonathan Ernst</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">Лидеры G7 во время совместного фотографирования перед рабочей встречей около Grand Prince Hotel в Хиросиме, Япони я</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="ap_photo" alt="Лидеры G7 во время совместного фотографирования перед рабочей встречей около Grand Prince Hotel в Хиросиме, Япония - Sputnik International, 1920, 21.05.2023" title="Лидеры G7 во время совместного фотографирования перед рабочей встречей около Grand Prince Hotel в Хиросиме, Япония" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110505668_0:239:2293:1529_1920x0_80_0_0_847a3b4b256fc9df180aa94875d9c9a2.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110505668_0:239:2293:1529_640x0_80_0_0_87491232c6cda94e8310317f2d2bd9bc.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110505668_0:239:2293:1529_1280x0_80_0_0_143a25e848cd7ce1950a979094c1a80a.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e7/05/15/1110505668_0:239:2293:1529_1920x0_80_0_0_847a3b4b256fc9df180aa94875d9c9a2.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © AP Photo / 乔纳森·恩斯特</div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据莫斯科（人造卫星）网报道：俄罗斯外交部周日表示，在日本举行的七国集团峰会上做出的政治化决定表明该集团已经“不可逆转地退化”。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “它（七国集团峰会）的主要结果是发表了一系列充满可恶的<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230520/russian-fm-lavrov-says-g7-summits-decisions-aimed-at-containing-russia-china-1110486721.html" target="_blank">反俄和反华言论</a>的声明。这是又一次导致发表旨在划定​​国际关系分界线的政治化声明的七国集团会议，”声明读。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">该部表示<a href="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/g7-leaders-on-shaky-ground-at-home-pummeled-by-low-approval-ratings--1110497390.html" target="_blank">，七国集团曾经是一个成员在各种重要国际问题上协调立场的组织</a>，而现在“它已经不可逆转地退化”。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “七国集团实际上已经专注于与俄罗斯的全面对抗。在美国的要求下，它承担了总部的角色，负责规划针对我国的制裁和其他混合战争工具，包括决定西方武器的规模和时机向基辅供应物资。这就是该组织今天存在的目的，”该部说。 </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110505682" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230521/moscow-says-g7-irreversibly-degraded-summits-decisions-politicized-1110505682.html?share-block=1110505685" data-title="&quot;The G7 has become literally fixated on a comprehensive confrontation with Russia. At the US' behest, it assumed the role of a headquarters for the planning of sanctions and other hybrid war tools against our country, including deciding the scale and timing of Western arms supplies to Kiev. That is the group's purpose of existing today,&quot; the ministry said. "></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 5 月 19 日至 21 日，日本广岛市举办了 G7 年度最高级别峰会。乌克兰总统沃洛德米尔·泽伦斯基受邀作为嘉宾，俄罗斯外交部表示，这最终将此次活动变成了一场“宣传秀”。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Sun, 21 May 2023 16:16:55 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/moscow-says-g7-irreversibly-degraded-summits-decisions-politicized-1110505682.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230521/moscow-says-g7-irreversibly-degraded-summits-decisions-politicized-1110505682.html<category>世界</category><category>G7</category><category>俄罗斯</category></item></channel></rss>